---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Get Started · Argus"
  description="用三步启动 Argus：写目标、启动 daemon、从看板监督研究。"
>
  <section class="page-hero compact">
    <div class="shell narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get started</p>
      <h1>你写目标，Argus 做研究。</h1>
      <p class="lede">任务规格只需要说清楚：要解决什么、什么算赢、预算与边界是什么。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="shell narrow">
      <div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">Step 1</p><h2>写一段 MISSION。</h2></div>
      <pre class="code-block"><code># MISSION
目标：把 &lt;metric&gt; 推到 &lt;target&gt;
范围：模型 / 数据 / GPU / 时间
完成：结果、代码、报告全部落盘
不做：明确排除的方向</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section surface">
    <div class="shell narrow">
      <div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">Step 2</p><h2>启动 daemon。</h2></div>
      <pre class="code-block"><code>argus-skill --daemon --continuous \
  --project-root &lt;项目目录&gt; \
  --objective "$(cat MISSION.md)"</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="shell narrow">
      <div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">Step 3</p><h2>看进度，不接管执行。</h2></div>
      <p>在看板中查看每个角色、mission、artifact 和 handoff；需要改变优先级时再发 operator 指令。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://dash.argusbot.cn">打开实时看板 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
